# Per-folder .gitignore for practical_2
# Ignore compiled binaries and generated outputs specific to this practical

# Executables and object files
*.o
*.exe
Problem*

# Generated output files
**/output.txt
**/outputs/
**/*_output.txt
*.out

# OS/editor artifacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# NOTE: These files are generated at build/run time and should not be committed.
